headline: Morgan Stanley initiates coverage of food stocks, BellRing Brands a top pick
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley initiated coverage of U.S. packaged food industry stocks in a note Monday, with a cautiously In-Line outlook, citing low earnings visibility and rising margin headwinds.
